t des Nachwende-Kinos in einem transnationalen Licht zu betrachten. Damit liefern sie zum ersten Mal eine systematische Untersuchung dieser Gattung und stellen sie als eine der wichtigsten Entwicklungen des gegenwärtigen Arthouse-Kinos heraus.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 03. Jan 2023) 4aArthouse-Kino. 4aBerliner Schule. 4aDeutsches Kino. 4aFilmemacher. 4aFilmkritik. 4aFilmtheorie. 4aGegenwartskino. 4aGlobales Kino. 4aGlobalisierung. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aNachwende-Kino. 4aNew Wave. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aBerlin School.  aContemporary Cinema.  aFilm Theory.  aGerman Cinema.  aGlobal Cinema.  aGlobalization.  aMedia Studies.  aMovie Critics.  aMovie Makers.  aNew Wave.  aPost-reunification Cinema.1 aAbel, Marco, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAbel, Marco, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aBaer, Hester, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBardan, Alice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCook, Roger F., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDassanowsky, Robert, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDjordjevic, Valentina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFech, Will, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFisher, Jaimey, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFisher, Jaimey, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGemünden, Gerd, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaegele, Lisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHomewood, Chris, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJaffe,